# Build-decision journal (LOCKED 2026-05-25): every build MAINTAINS implementation-notes.md
# at repo root, but it is LOCAL-ONLY scratch — the Pre-Ship Grep Gate hard-fails on a committed
# root/source copy ([implementation-notes-placement]). Anchored to root so the gate's exempt
# _verification/implementation-notes.* copy stays tracked.
/implementation-notes.md
/implementation-notes.html

# _verification/ is QA + review scratch, not source. No screenshots (PNG) or per-route raw
# data are tracked: the visual-QA bundles regenerate every `npm run qa:brand:visual`
# (~220MB/run), and the rest are one-off review crops/captures. All stay on disk for local
# review but out of git. Reviewable TEXT artifacts stay tracked (visual-qa-summary.*,
# manual-visual-review.md, *-audit.*, brand-closure-qa.*, *.html review docs). Durable image
# proof belongs in R2 (bwm-evidence-bundles/), not git.
_verification/**/*.png
_verification/**/metrics.json
_verification/**/browser-events.json

# build journal — Stage-2 artifact, never committed (Pre-Ship gate forbids it)
implementation-notes.md
